WEBVTT

00:05.012 --> 00:07.482
They got nerve.
Right in front of the sign.

00:08.034 --> 00:10.834
Looks like the city
just made an easy $85.

00:13.313 --> 00:14.423
What are you doing?

00:15.110 --> 00:16.655
This place got held up yesterday.

00:16.752 --> 00:18.584
I remember. I took the call.

00:19.035 --> 00:20.093
Looks pretty quiet.

00:21.090 --> 00:22.826
Damn pen's out of ink.

00:23.212 --> 00:24.215
Use mine.

00:24.459 --> 00:25.462
Forget it.

00:26.023 --> 00:27.431
Let's just grab some chili.

00:29.624 --> 00:30.627
Funny,

00:31.017 --> 00:33.232
whoever owns that car has no idea.

00:33.601 --> 00:35.316
Tonight was their lucky night.

